# Initial Restful planning of Tour and Travel
1Ô∏è AUTH & USER MANAGEMENT
Auth
POST   /api/auth/register
POST   /api/auth/login
POST   /api/auth/logout
GET    /api/auth/me

Users 
GET    /api/users/me                 ‚Üí logged-in user profile
PUT    /api/users/me                 ‚Üí update own profile
PUT    /api/users/me/profile-image   ‚Üí update profile image

Admin ‚Äì User Management
GET    /api/admin/users
GET    /api/admin/users/:userId
PUT    /api/admin/users/:userId
PATCH  /api/admin/users/:userId/block
PATCH  /api/admin/users/:userId/role
DELETE /api/admin/users/:userId

2Ô∏è DESTINATIONS
GET    /api/destinations
GET    /api/destinations/:destinationId

Admin
POST   /api/admin/destinations
PUT    /api/admin/destinations/:destinationId
DELETE /api/admin/destinations/:destinationId

3Ô∏è TOUR PACKAGES
GET    /api/tours
GET    /api/tours/:tourId

Admin ‚Äì Tour Management
POST   /api/admin/tours
PUT    /api/admin/tours/:tourId
DELETE /api/admin/tours/:tourId

Tour Images
POST   /api/admin/tours/:tourId/images
DELETE /api/admin/tours/:tourId/images/:imageId

Tour Itineraries (Admin-defined)
GET    /api/tours/:tourId/itinerary

Admin
POST   /api/admin/tours/:tourId/itinerary
PUT    /api/admin/itinerary/:itineraryId
DELETE /api/admin/itinerary/:itineraryId

4Ô∏è TOUR SCHEDULES
GET    /api/tours/:tourId/schedules

Admin
POST   /api/admin/tours/:tourId/schedules
PUT    /api/admin/schedules/:scheduleId
DELETE /api/admin/schedules/:scheduleId

5Ô∏è BOOKINGS & PAYMENTS (TOUR)
